title: Winter Cottaging - How to enjoy your cottage all year round - EP
description:
Pages: 80 pages
Publisher: Cottage Life Media Inc. (23 October 2012)
Language: English
ASIN: B009NG3OSC
ISBN: 0988066637 
ISBN-13: 9780988066632 
Format: EPUB



New cottages are almost always built for four-season use; more cottagers are winterizing their older buildings too. It's never been easier to use the cottage in winter, but the season brings a special set of problems and questions. What's the best way to protect the building and the plumbing from the cold and the ice? What are these odd tracks and unfamiliar noises? How well will our gear survive if we leave it all winter? Here is a collection of our favourite questions from Cottage Life magazine readers and answers from experts, about one of the most rewarding times of year.
